==结构==
硫化铜（靛铜矿）以六方晶系形式结晶，也存在一种不定型的高压形式，<ref>{{cite journal
| last =  Peiris
| first = M
| coauthors = Sweeney, J.S.; Campbell, A.J.; Heinz D. L.
| year = 1996
| title = Pressure-induced amorphization of covellite, CuS
| journal = J. Chem. Phys.
| volume = 104
| issue = 
| pages = 11–16
| doi = 10.1063/1.470870 }}</ref> 是以[[拉曼光譜學|拉曼光譜學]]为基础，被描述为一种扭曲的靛铜矿形式的结构。由铜(II)[[乙二胺|乙二胺]][[配合物|配合物]]与[[硫脲|硫脲]]在常温下反应也可得一种不定型的半导体硫化铜，在30°C时转化为靛铜矿结构。<ref>{{cite journal
| last =  Grijalva
| first = H. 
| coauthors = Inoue, M.; Boggavarapu, S.; Calvert, P. 
| year = 1996
| title = Amorphous and crystalline copper sulfides, CuS
| journal = J. Mater. Chem. 
| volume = 6
| issue = 
| pages = 1157–1160
| doi = 10.1039/JM9960601157}}</ref><br />
硫化铜的晶体结构被多次报道。<ref>{{cite journal
